{
  "texts": [
    "We compare the MPA with diverse baselines in E2E driving algorithms that fall in the two following categories.",
    "(1) Pretrained base policy with open-loop training manner: we compare with the performance of UniAD[3], VAD[4] and LTF[2] on the HUGSIM dataset.",
    "We further build on our MPA with these policies.",
